{
  "id": "RAW_8f810e25",
  "title": "Qwen3 变身扩散语言模型？不从零训练也能跑，30B 参数创纪录",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2650994927&idx=2&sn=abb637d57d22a7c5b334b8cad2cf4b85",
  "date": "2025-10-12 04:02:00",
